## Getting Started

```bash
# Install dependencies for all sub-projects
make deps

# Run all sub-projects in dependency order
make build

# Run a specific sub-project
cd {{ sub_projects[0].name if sub_projects else 'my_project' }} && dbt run
```

## Architecture

This project uses [dbt Mesh](https://docs.getdbt.com/best-practices/how-we-mesh/mesh-1-intro)
to organize models across multiple projects with explicit contracts and access controls.

- **Public** models (marts) are accessible to downstream projects via `{{ '{{' }} ref('project', 'model') {{ '}}' }}`
- **Protected** models (staging) are accessible within the same project only
- **Private** models (intermediate) are not accessible outside their group
